{"tid":656983,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[私家醫院見工] 轉工面試, 第1次one on one見HR求指教","createTime":"2018-05-07T16:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T07:32:11.000Z","uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b4b34353aa03284a0c3f46cbc632448af0efb223","tid":656983,"uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T16:54:05.000Z","msg":"細佬我做緊d輔助醫療post<br />\n近排想放棄醫管局, 入面d人太垃圾糜爛, D老細又蠢又怕事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚟緊會去私院interview<br />\n今個星期會去HR department, one on one同HR manager見<br />\n細佬我第1次出去見識個世界, 之前未試過同HR隻揪<br />\n有冇人可以比d tips我指教下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢就剩係叫我帶學歷同工作證明<br />\n我準備佐個self intro(打算中英各準備1個3分鐘, 1個5分鐘) <br />\nself intro講自己d work exp, 個HR又聽唔聽得明d專業野架????<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人工我就唔洗提出架喇, 因為都係跟pt scale, 番工日子都度好<br />\n<br />\n仲要prepare d 咩呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d923ca0578b4d6cd0f683e46d709d81b08b96c8","tid":656983,"uid":74171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:00:53.000Z","msg":"諗下點答啲八搭鳩問題：&quot;點解我要請你? &quot;之類"},{"pid":"90a4ed36746dcbb002bdd3c2bee86073b9f4d3c9","tid":656983,"uid":104965,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:06:12.000Z","msg":"同佢講你係連登仔<br />\nFg 月入最少30k 果隻<br />\n<br />\n咁佢就識點樣同你簽contract 嫁啦"},{"pid":"d217f76ce28f8138b4740f31fc8bc9f5a8ef72d5","tid":656983,"uid":180716,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:11:39.000Z","msg":"點解要請你  你有咩優勝過人嘅地方  你對醫院有咩認識  你對醫院有咩貢獻  點解揀呢間唔揀第間<br />\n同埋prep埋自己cv可能會問下你以前啲野<br />\n總之都係prep大路野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e1984a6cca28588f91e3acc83c9e27d12e9002","tid":656983,"uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:13:42.000Z","msg":"其實醫院d hr係咪會搵番特定人負責某幾個department?<br />\n我驚我prepare太多專業既野講<br />\n但原來個HR都唔知我講乜9"},{"pid":"720950a995e407666d14c3fa8ae4d025ef33e37a","tid":656983,"uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:15:14.000Z","msg":"btw, 其實department in charge已經見過我, 佢都講佐話想要我, 希望我見HR順利<br />\n我估都踏佐半隻腳入去架喇<br />\n<br />\n但都唔想太大安旨意, pre好去見埋HR"},{"pid":"f57620c7e398dfc53d2a9c3cefeaf53912085573","tid":656983,"uid":1473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:16:56.000Z","msg":"Hr 陪坐嫁咋，dom/manager 先係負責in 你個個"},{"pid":"54ac0c245da6b0d40dda667805429c4cd8a7de29","tid":656983,"uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90a4ed36746dcbb002bdd3c2bee86073b9f4d3c9","tid":656983,"uid":104965,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:06:12.000Z","msg":"同佢講你係連登仔<br />\nFg 月入最少30k 果隻<br />\n<br />\n咁佢就識點樣同你簽contract 嫁啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:17:17.000Z","msg":"其實allied health 入HA fg都係差唔多30k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw, 其實我地呢d係跟年資排pt scale, 人工其實都唔係太洗傾, 都係跟醫院規矩<br />\n除非佢計少佐你年資"},{"pid":"e9049e133b0616a456c037e363852b0774764d0a","tid":656983,"uid":70357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90a4ed36746dcbb002bdd3c2bee86073b9f4d3c9","tid":656983,"uid":104965,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:06:12.000Z","msg":"同佢講你係連登仔<br />\nFg 月入最少30k 果隻<br />\n<br />\n咁佢就識點樣同你簽contract 嫁啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:17:19.000Z","msg":"輔助醫療入私院我諗係有30k<br />\n係連登仔"},{"pid":"0c6de9210be8121786239bd6471843b233180d02","tid":656983,"uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f57620c7e398dfc53d2a9c3cefeaf53912085573","tid":656983,"uid":1473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:16:56.000Z","msg":"Hr 陪坐嫁咋，dom/manager 先係負責in 你個個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:17:43.000Z","msg":"btw, 其實department in charge已經見過我, 佢都講佐話想要我, 希望我見HR順利<br />\n我估都踏佐半隻腳入去架喇<br />\n<br />\n但都唔想太大安旨意, pre好去見埋HR"},{"p